---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Registry">
  <h1>Registry</h1>

  <p>SQLite-backed persistence layer for agents, versions, evaluation history, and test cases.</p>

  <h2>Database Location</h2>
  <pre><code># Default
.agent-forge/registry.db

# Custom
AGENT_FORGE_DATA=/path/to/data agent-forge create "..."</code></pre>

  <h2>Schema</h2>
  <pre><code>agents
  id          TEXT PRIMARY KEY
  name        TEXT UNIQUE NOT NULL
  description TEXT
  created_at  DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
  latest_version INTEGER DEFAULT 0

agent_versions
  id          TEXT PRIMARY KEY
  agent_id    TEXT REFERENCES agents(id) ON DELETE CASCADE
  version     INTEGER NOT NULL
  code        TEXT NOT NULL
  created_at  DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
  UNIQUE(agent_id, version)

eval_runs
  id                  TEXT PRIMARY KEY
  agent_version_id    TEXT REFERENCES agent_versions(id) ON DELETE CASCADE
  iteration           INTEGER NOT NULL
  test_pass_rate      REAL
  judge_score         REAL
  composite_score     REAL
  passed              INTEGER
  failure_report      TEXT  -- JSON
  created_at          DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP

test_cases
  id              TEXT PRIMARY KEY
  agent_id        TEXT REFERENCES agents(id) ON DELETE CASCADE
  input_json      TEXT NOT NULL
  expected_schema TEXT NOT NULL
  traced_to       TEXT  -- JSON array
  diversity_score REAL
  created_at      DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP</code></pre>

  <h2>Key Functions</h2>
  <pre><code>// Agents
createAgent(name: string, description: string): AgentRow
getAgentByName(name: string): AgentRow | null
getAllAgents(): AgentRow[]

// Versions
createAgentVersion(agentId: string, version: number, code: string): VersionRow
getAgentVersion(agentId: string, version: number): VersionRow | null
getLatestAgentVersion(agentId: string): VersionRow | null
getAllAgentVersions(agentId: string): VersionRow[]

// Evals
createEvalRun(params: EvalParams): EvalRunRow
getEvalRunsForVersion(agentVersionId: string): EvalRunRow[]
getBestEvalForAgent(agentId: string): EvalRunRow | null

// Test Cases
createTestCase(params: TestCaseParams): TestCaseRow
getTestCasesForAgent(agentId: string): TestCaseRow[]
deleteTestCasesForAgent(agentId: string): void</code></pre>

  <h2>Usage in LoopController</h2>
  <pre><code>// On each iteration:
const version = createAgentVersion(agentId, iter, code);
createEvalRun({'{'}
  agentVersionId: version.id,
  iteration: iter,
  testPassRate: report.testPassRate,
  judgeScore: report.judgeScore,
  compositeScore: report.composite,
  passed: gateResult.passed,
  failureReport: {'{'} failures, warnings {'}'},
{'}'});

// Best score tracked across iterations
if (report.composite {'>'} bestScore) {'{'}
  bestScore = report.composite;
  bestCode = code;
{'}'}</code></pre>

  <h2>aiosqlite Notes</h2>
  <p>The registry uses <code>bun:sqlite</code> (Bun's native SQLite bindings). WAL mode is enabled for concurrent read access. Foreign keys are enforced via CASCADE deletes.</p>
</Layout>
